decks.notes: The main idea of this deck is to overwhelm the opponent with a fast and aggressive approach. Adeline, Resplendent Cathar serves as the commander, leading a battalion of efficient creatures and powerful spells geared towards combat. The deck is full of low-cost creatures with abilities that support each other and pump each other up, creating a formidable army that can quickly take down the opponent's life total. There are also several spells aimed at protecting the creatures and disrupting the opponent's game plan. With a strong focus on white weenies and combat tricks, the deck aims to apply constant pressure on the opponent and win the game before the opponent can stabilize.

The key concept of this deck is to maintain control over the game by countering and removing threats while gradually gaining card advantage. The deck utilizes a variety of counterspells and removal spells, such as Force Spike, Spell Snare, Condemn, and Swords to Plowshares, to prevent opponents from resolving impactful spells or creatures. It also includes card draw spells like Wall of Omens and Faithful Mending to replenish the player's resources. With the commander, Shorikai, Genesis Engine, the deck can further manipulate the game state by exiling opponents' cards or returning them to their hand. In addition to control elements, the deck includes win conditions like Dream Trawler and True-Name Nemesis to close out the game once the player has established control.
